1
00:00:58,410 --> 00:01:02,370
♪ The past is buried with farewell tears ♪

2
00:01:02,540 --> 00:01:06,000
♪ Tang’s belief is regained in the Soul Land ♪

3
00:01:06,330 --> 00:01:09,250
♪ Ghostly Trace, from place to place you run ♪

4
00:01:09,750 --> 00:01:12,000
♪ Xuan Tian power burns ♪

5
00:01:12,280 --> 00:01:15,690
♪ Never look down at the shabby wooden house ♪

6
00:01:16,170 --> 00:01:19,400
♪ Create our glorious miracles in the Soul Land ♪

7
00:01:19,960 --> 00:01:23,090
♪ When seven creatures combine,
hope is what we get ♪

8
00:01:23,340 --> 00:01:26,580
♪ Never give up as it’ll be unforgettable ♪

9
00:01:26,580 --> 00:01:31,250
♪ For a hundred thousand years
I’ll search and grow with you ♪

10
00:01:31,500 --> 00:01:37,750
♪ I’ll turn into a sky of bright stars
when I think of you ♪

11
00:01:38,960 --> 00:01:42,150
♪ Life is full of wars, battles, adventures ♪

12
00:01:42,530 --> 00:01:45,530
♪ and I’ll still protect you ♪

13
00:01:45,960 --> 00:01:51,670
♪ I’m still the King no matter
the Black and Blue are awakened or not ♪

14
00:01:52,270 --> 00:01:55,900
♪ The darkness is all released
by clouds and mists ♪

15
00:01:56,360 --> 00:01:59,570
♪ I’ll never forget my promise ♪

16
00:02:00,020 --> 00:02:02,690
♪ even if the sky and earth changes
or the sea roars ♪

17
00:02:03,010 --> 00:02:07,970
♪ I’ll stand up high even the Gods have to look up ♪

18
00:02:08,660 --> 00:02:13,540
♪ My invincible legend right on this Soul Land ♪

19
00:02:29,560 --> 00:02:32,630
[This animation is based on the novel Soul Land]
[written by Tangjia Sanshao]

20
00:02:32,760 --> 00:02:34,400
[Previous Episode]
Little San, you’re finally back.

21
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:36,420
Brother San, where are the gifts?

22
00:02:36,420 --> 00:02:37,460
Hurry and show us.

23
00:02:37,460 --> 00:02:40,640
This herb is called
Lovesick Heartbroken Scarlet.

24
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:44,780
I’m not single-minded.
I have no fate with this flower.

25
00:02:45,180 --> 00:02:48,060
Seems like I still can’t let it go.

26
00:02:48,660 --> 00:02:52,920
Brother, that legend must be true, right?

27
00:02:52,920 --> 00:02:56,960
Five levels. My soul power
has increased by five levels.

28
00:02:56,960 --> 00:02:58,000
Look.

29
00:02:58,000 --> 00:03:01,000
Your Qibao Amber Pagoda
has nine levels now.

30
00:03:03,950 --> 00:03:08,830
[Soul Land]
[Episode 54]

31
00:03:34,060 --> 00:03:37,260
Zhu Qing, what about your soul power?

32
00:03:37,260 --> 00:03:40,160
I think it has increased by seven levels.

33
00:03:40,160 --> 00:03:40,920
Unbelievable.

34
00:03:40,920 --> 00:03:43,760
Your Daffodil Jade Beauty is better than us.

35
00:03:43,760 --> 00:03:47,080
Little San is right. It suits you very much.

36
00:03:47,080 --> 00:03:51,500
But this is originally for you, I...

37
00:03:52,860 --> 00:03:54,800
It supposed to be yours.

38
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:57,220
I have Lovesick Heartbroken Scarlet with me.

39
00:03:57,220 --> 00:03:59,160
I’m worried that you would envy me.

40
00:04:20,760 --> 00:04:24,240
Did you feel the majestic vibes in my flame?

41
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:26,320
My Phoenix flame is purer.

42
00:04:26,320 --> 00:04:29,280
I’m finally a true Phoenix Soul Master.

43
00:04:29,280 --> 00:04:32,120
This Fatty is boasting again.

44
00:05:00,700 --> 00:05:05,200
Hey, let me go.

45
00:05:08,760 --> 00:05:12,180
It is doubtless that you care for me.
Are you still leaving?

46
00:05:12,180 --> 00:05:14,040
I’ll not let you go anymore.

47
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:23,280
Leave these sweet talks to your lovers.

48
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:28,560
Zhu Qing, didn’t you realize that
I’ve been as pure as Tang San lately?

49
00:05:30,700 --> 00:05:36,940
Until you’re as innocent as Brother San,
then only we’ll see.

50
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:41,440
Little San, thank you.

51
00:05:41,440 --> 00:05:43,900
I’ve finally broken through
the bottleneck of Level 40.

52
00:05:43,900 --> 00:05:45,260
By the way,

53
00:05:45,260 --> 00:05:47,040
when you’re available can you teach me

54
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:50,420
how to be pure and innocent?

55
00:05:50,800 --> 00:05:53,100
I’m afraid that you don’t have the chance.

56
00:05:53,100 --> 00:05:54,420
That’s right, Mr. Dai.

57
00:05:54,420 --> 00:05:59,580
Only my brother can be considered
as the pure and innocent Mr. Tang San.

58
00:06:23,260 --> 00:06:26,020
Master, how do you feel?

59
00:06:27,280 --> 00:06:29,700
It has been more than thirty years...

60
00:06:29,700 --> 00:06:33,300
Unexpectedly, the bottleneck
which has haunted my whole life,

61
00:06:33,300 --> 00:06:36,100
I’ve broken through it today.

62
00:06:38,580 --> 00:06:40,860
Grade Nine Purple Mushroom...

63
00:06:40,860 --> 00:06:44,160
Seems like I’ve underestimated
the benefits of the external force.

64
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:47,320
Master, you’ve broken through Level 30.

65
00:06:47,320 --> 00:06:48,600
Congratulations.

66
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:52,800
Maybe your practice will
advance in leaps and bounds later.

67
00:06:53,760 --> 00:06:55,200
The practice of a soul master

68
00:06:55,200 --> 00:06:59,560
will be harder as we age.

69
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:01,000
How many years I have left?

70
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:04,200
I’ve given up the hope to be a powerful soul master.

71
00:07:04,200 --> 00:07:06,920
You are my only hope.

72
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:10,740
Okay, from now on, practice properly.

73
00:07:10,740 --> 00:07:12,940
Keep on absorbing to strengthen your power.

74
00:07:12,940 --> 00:07:14,860
Don’t eager for quick results.

75
00:07:14,860 --> 00:07:17,960
Seven days later,
I’ll hunt for a soul beast with Mu Bai

76
00:07:17,960 --> 00:07:18,880
to obtain soul rings.

77
00:07:18,880 --> 00:07:20,440
Okay.

78
00:07:35,820 --> 00:07:37,120
Rong Rong, Little Ao, be careful.

79
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:40,180
First soul skill,
White Tiger Protection Barrier.

80
00:07:44,900 --> 00:07:46,560
Be careful, everyone.

81
00:07:51,580 --> 00:07:52,900
Scatter.

82
00:07:55,520 --> 00:07:56,880
Fly.

83
00:07:56,880 --> 00:07:58,660
Flying Mushroom Sausage.

84
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:21,020
Jiubao famously said,
First Strength Second Speed.

85
00:08:29,100 --> 00:08:31,260
First soul skill, Arched Body.

86
00:08:34,820 --> 00:08:36,740
Second soul skill, Nether White Claws.

87
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:55,060
Second soul skill,
White Tiger Intense Light Wave.

88
00:08:55,060 --> 00:08:57,620
First soul skill, Phoenix Firing Line.

89
00:08:57,620 --> 00:09:00,640
Stop, I’m Teacher Zhao.

90
00:09:00,640 --> 00:09:03,000
Third soul skill,
Constraint of Spider Web.

91
00:09:20,400 --> 00:09:25,460
It’s really Teacher Zhao.
Why are you attacking us?

92
00:09:26,200 --> 00:09:28,100
I just want to test your abilities.

93
00:09:28,100 --> 00:09:30,000
Who knows that you would be this fierce?

94
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:33,080
But, you’ve greatly improved.

95
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:36,100
As your teacher, I’m very satisfied.

96
00:09:36,100 --> 00:09:38,000
I’m sorry, Teacher Zhao.

97
00:09:40,360 --> 00:09:42,580
Xiao Gang, I lost.

98
00:09:42,580 --> 00:09:46,680
Seems like if they join forces,
they can defeat Zhao Wu Ji.

99
00:09:47,740 --> 00:09:50,660
But I have no money currently,
I’ll put this on credit.

100
00:09:50,660 --> 00:09:53,740
Hey, you’re making a bet on me?

101
00:09:53,740 --> 00:09:57,100
Wait, what do you mean
that they can beat me?

102
00:09:57,100 --> 00:09:58,660
I was just being lenient on them.

103
00:09:58,660 --> 00:10:00,640
If you don’t believe it,
we shall fight again.

104
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:09,460
Enough, don’t be too carried away.

105
00:10:09,460 --> 00:10:12,000
The enemy who wants to take your lives away

106
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:14,600
will not show any mercy.

107
00:10:14,600 --> 00:10:16,220
By the way, Little San,

108
00:10:17,480 --> 00:10:19,920
Senior Dugu is looking for you.

109
00:10:19,920 --> 00:10:21,920
<i>Old Freak is looking for me?</i>

110
00:10:41,150 --> 00:10:46,550
[Soul Land]

111
00:11:10,600 --> 00:11:12,700
Little Freak, you’re here.

112
00:11:16,360 --> 00:11:19,840
Little San, I’ll leave first.

113
00:11:21,560 --> 00:11:25,380
Grandpa, why did you call this scum over?

114
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:29,720
Besides, why are you being an adviser
at this lousy school?

115
00:11:29,720 --> 00:11:33,080
Even so, you should go to Tian Dou Imperial School.

116
00:11:33,080 --> 00:11:37,920
Enough, Yan Yan. Don’t call him scum anymore.

117
00:11:37,920 --> 00:11:39,280
Look at you.

118
00:11:39,280 --> 00:11:42,640
You’ve grown up,
but you’re still acting like a child.

119
00:11:42,640 --> 00:11:47,900
Tang San is younger,
yet he’s more mature than you.

120
00:11:48,380 --> 00:11:50,760
What’s good about him?

121
00:11:50,760 --> 00:11:52,620
I was just too careless previously.

122
00:11:52,620 --> 00:11:53,640
If given another chance,

123
00:11:53,640 --> 00:11:55,960
I’ll hit him hard.

124
00:11:57,360 --> 00:11:59,060
Then you must hurry.

125
00:11:59,060 --> 00:12:03,080
Six months later, there’ll be a
National Advanced Soul Master School Contest.

126
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:05,160
We’re both in the Tian Dou area.

127
00:12:05,160 --> 00:12:07,240
We’ll meet soon.

128
00:12:07,240 --> 00:12:09,480
You! Wait for it.

129
00:12:09,480 --> 00:12:13,120
Previously you raided Tian Heng,
I’ll not let you get away with this.

130
00:12:13,120 --> 00:12:16,360
Little Freak, I don’t care about the others.

131
00:12:16,360 --> 00:12:18,580
But you must not hurt my granddaughter.

132
00:12:18,580 --> 00:12:21,580
Or else, I’ll not let you go.

133
00:12:21,580 --> 00:12:24,720
Grandpa, how can he hurt me?

134
00:12:24,720 --> 00:12:27,720
You’re encouraging him
and discouraging me.

135
00:12:27,720 --> 00:12:29,240
You’re siding with him.

136
00:12:29,240 --> 00:12:31,620
Did you accept him as your disciple?

137
00:12:32,740 --> 00:12:38,180
Yan Yan, do you know
what level his soul power is currently?

138
00:12:38,180 --> 00:12:43,180
Level 37, it’s just about yours.

139
00:12:43,180 --> 00:12:48,860
In just six months, this Little Freak
may pass the bottleneck of Level 40.

140
00:12:48,860 --> 00:12:51,740
You’re a soul master of
Controlling Branch like him.

141
00:12:51,740 --> 00:12:53,540
But I’m certain that

142
00:12:53,540 --> 00:12:56,220
you can’t beat him.

143
00:12:56,220 --> 00:12:58,840
If you underestimate this Little Freak,

144
00:12:58,840 --> 00:13:01,960
you’ll face great loss.

145
00:13:04,880 --> 00:13:08,720
About my ability, we’ll see on the ring.

146
00:13:10,280 --> 00:13:13,400
Old Freak, this is the medicine that I’ve made.

147
00:13:15,180 --> 00:13:16,900
After obtaining the soul bone for her,

148
00:13:16,900 --> 00:13:20,220
you’ll need to feed her once
around midnight for seven days.

149
00:13:20,220 --> 00:13:23,200
Just direct the poison into the soul bone.

150
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:26,240
I’ll leave first, I’ll visit you later.

151
00:13:28,720 --> 00:13:32,520
Little Freak, my wish has come true.

152
00:13:32,520 --> 00:13:34,600
It’s time to leave.

153
00:13:35,780 --> 00:13:37,520
You’re leaving?

154
00:13:38,240 --> 00:13:40,860
I need to take care of something.

155
00:13:40,860 --> 00:13:45,020
If I’m back in time, maybe I can catch your contest.

156
00:13:45,020 --> 00:13:49,080
But don’t forget, you must not hurt Yan Yan.

157
00:13:49,080 --> 00:13:52,700
For your sake, I won’t do her any harm.

158
00:13:52,700 --> 00:13:55,540
But, please remind her that

159
00:13:55,540 --> 00:13:57,660
don’t try to provoke me.

160
00:13:57,660 --> 00:14:02,320
Old Freak, take care of yourself.
Don’t forget about the two iron balls.

161
00:14:03,840 --> 00:14:05,840
You must take care of yourself too.

162
00:14:14,660 --> 00:14:19,840
Little San, Frander and Er Long will follow me
and Mu Bai to hunt a soul beast.

163
00:14:19,840 --> 00:14:22,020
We’ll leave the school for a few days.

164
00:14:22,020 --> 00:14:24,600
You’ll study with
the advance class during this period.

165
00:14:24,600 --> 00:14:26,100
Don’t slack off.

166
00:14:26,100 --> 00:14:29,980
Don’t worry, Master. We’ll practice hard.

167
00:14:29,980 --> 00:14:32,920
Little San, I will go home too.

168
00:14:35,360 --> 00:14:37,900
I’ll entrust Xiao Wu to you.

169
00:14:48,540 --> 00:14:51,440
Goodbye, have a safe journey.

170
00:14:52,020 --> 00:14:54,200
Let’s go to class.

171
00:15:03,880 --> 00:15:06,660
They are from Tian Dou Imperial School.

172
00:15:06,660 --> 00:15:09,220
They’re so proud and rude.
They’re really annoying.

173
00:15:10,660 --> 00:15:13,240
During the Advanced Soul Master School Contest,

174
00:15:13,240 --> 00:15:14,680
we must show them

175
00:15:14,680 --> 00:15:17,460
Shrek School’s ability.

176
00:15:34,540 --> 00:15:37,580
Hey, where is my design?

177
00:15:38,280 --> 00:15:42,420
Where is it? It was with me just now.

178
00:15:42,420 --> 00:15:46,140
Gosh, I’ve lost my new school uniform design.

179
00:15:47,400 --> 00:15:49,740
Goodbye, Dean.

180
00:15:49,740 --> 00:15:52,060
Never mind, I’ll design a new one.

181
00:15:52,060 --> 00:15:54,500
Thank goodness that the essence of the design

182
00:15:54,500 --> 00:15:56,780
is all in my mind.

183
00:16:04,940 --> 00:16:07,280
Little San, although our ability is stronger,

184
00:16:07,280 --> 00:16:09,760
we lose in terms of appearance.

185
00:16:09,760 --> 00:16:12,700
That’s right. We’re in a deep pit
in terms of appearance.

186
00:16:12,700 --> 00:16:16,560
Totally trampled and absolutely squashed.

187
00:16:24,220 --> 00:16:26,140
This indescribable colour.

188
00:16:26,140 --> 00:16:27,680
This unimaginable design.

189
00:16:27,680 --> 00:16:31,940
I can’t believe that
Dean Frander has such a poor taste.

190
00:16:33,840 --> 00:16:38,000
Imagine us wearing this new uniform
to the soul master contest later.

191
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:40,480
In front of thousands of audiences.

192
00:16:56,220 --> 00:16:58,920
By the way, you’ve been practicing in school.

193
00:16:58,920 --> 00:17:01,840
Is there any difference
in terms of teaching methods?

194
00:17:01,840 --> 00:17:06,720
There are no big differences.
But there are a lot of female soul masters.

195
00:17:06,720 --> 00:17:10,540
It is rumored that they’re here because
they admire Deputy Dean Er Long.

196
00:17:11,060 --> 00:17:12,540
There are six classes in the school.

197
00:17:12,540 --> 00:17:15,480
It is arranged according
to the level of soul power.

198
00:17:16,180 --> 00:17:18,480
If you reach a certain level
you can skip grades.

199
00:17:18,480 --> 00:17:20,300
We’re all above Level 30.

200
00:17:20,300 --> 00:17:22,420
We’re all in the advance class.

201
00:17:24,880 --> 00:17:28,060
There are over thirty students
in advance class including us.

202
00:17:28,060 --> 00:17:30,340
But most of them are older than us.

203
00:17:30,340 --> 00:17:31,520
People like them,

204
00:17:31,520 --> 00:17:33,220
how can they be a Grand Soul Land Master?

205
00:17:33,220 --> 00:17:35,460
Okay, Brother.
Let’s not waste time talking to them.

206
00:17:35,460 --> 00:17:37,580
Let’s go, I’ll show you the classroom.

207
00:17:57,020 --> 00:17:58,200
Tai Long.

208
00:18:14,280 --> 00:18:15,700
This...

209
00:20:41,780 --> 00:20:44,480
[Next Episode]
Brother, look. What is that?

210
00:20:44,480 --> 00:20:45,780
Do you want to break in?

211
00:20:45,780 --> 00:20:47,420
Then come on.

212
00:20:50,160 --> 00:20:52,500
Brother, there’s a lot of good food in Tian Dou City.

213
00:20:52,500 --> 00:20:54,660
Let’s tour around, please?

214
00:20:54,660 --> 00:20:56,720
Then we shall put this up for auction.

215
00:20:56,720 --> 00:20:59,520
Brother, Tai Long keeps pestering me.

216
00:20:59,520 --> 00:21:01,160
He pesters you?

217
00:21:01,160 --> 00:21:04,100
Is he stronger than Boss Dai?

218
00:21:04,100 --> 00:21:05,700
Seems like we need to be careful.

219
00:21:07,040 --> 00:21:08,040
If you win,

220
00:21:08,040 --> 00:21:11,260
I’ll admit that you’re qualified to sit here.

